1. *Krug* je geometrijska figura. (The circle is a geometric figure.)
2. *Krugovi* se mogu preklapati jedni preko drugih. (Circles can overlap with each other.)
3. On je stvorio *krug* oko sebe. (He created a circle around himself.)
4. *Kružio* je gradom bez cilja. (He was wandering around the city without a destination.)
5. Ona je *kružila* okolo automobila. (She was circling around the car.)
6. On je obišao *krug* i vratio se na isto mesto. (He went around in a circle and returned to the same place.)